entries.femaleVariant: The response to Kulikowski's latest work is overwhelming.
Kulikowski's derivative to the point of absurdity. Nothing new to say at all.
Sorry, but I can't let a comment like that go. Maybe you just don't understand his message.
His latest work is a brilliant investigation into the medial status of the canvas itself.
Precisely. He's calling into question the tenuous relationship between referent and reference.
